			<p class="lead">Swiggy Instamart is one of India&rsquo;s largest
				and fastest-growing quick-commerce platforms, delivering groceries
				and everyday essentials in minutes from a dense network of dark
				stores. For brands, it is one of the highest-potential channels in
				the country &mdash; but getting onboarded is very different from
				listing on a marketplace.</p>
			<p>Now a standalone brand within the Swiggy group, Instamart has
				grown into one of the country&rsquo;s defining quick-commerce
				players &mdash; carrying a catalogue of tens of thousands of
				products, operating across more than a hundred cities, and serving
				millions of customers every month who reorder everyday essentials in
				minutes. For a brand, an early and well-executed presence on this
				channel unlocks a large, high-frequency, repeat-purchase audience
				that is very hard to reach at the same speed through traditional
				retail or slower online channels.</p>
			<p>
				Unlike a typical seller platform, Instamart runs on a <strong>B2B
					supply model</strong>: Swiggy buys your products into its dark stores and
				retails them to customers. That means onboarding involves supplier
				empanelment, a rigorous per-SKU catalogue-approval process called
				NPI, Category Manager negotiation, and multi-city compliance. Done
				right, it is a powerful growth engine; done wrong, brands stall for
				months. This is where IARDO comes in.
			</p>
			<p>
				IARDO provides <strong>end-to-end Swiggy Instamart
					onboarding services across PAN India</strong>. As an authorized Amazon
				Seller Acquisition Partner operating since 2016 under founder Manish
				Madan, we have onboarded 2500+ brands across marketplaces and
				quick-commerce platforms &mdash; and we bring that same expertise to
				your Instamart launch. Whether you need a reliable <strong>Swiggy
					Instamart onboarding agency</strong>, help with <strong>Instamart
					supplier registration</strong>, or simply want to know how to sell on Swiggy
				Instamart, this page covers the full process, documents, timelines,
				cities, and exactly how IARDO gets you live.
			</p>

